name: Guidebook NYC
title: Hippodrome au Pont de l'Alma
creator: Elaine Lustig Cohen
summary: This NYC guidebook sets itself apart from others of its time by highlighting more unusual or lesser known aspects of the city’s people, places and attractions. As author Kate Simon puts it, the visitors can discover “the beat and the offbeat, the ordinary and the bizarre.”

name: Nuclear Policy
title: Hippodrome au Pont de l'Alma
creator: Saul Bass
font: assets/fonts/Neue Haas Grotesk Display Pro 65 Medium.otf
summary: SANE was founded in 1957 as a response to nuclear bomb testing and the arms race. Its mission was to “develop public support for a boldly conceived and executed policy which will lead mankind away from war and toward justice and peace,” seeking to keep nuclear power within safe and human bounds.
